abstract: NHL Roundup; New York Rangers defeat Detroit Red Wings, 1-0; other hockey scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Henrik Lundqvist made 22 saves, and Kevin Klein scored the game’s only goal, less than two minutes into overtime, leading the Rangers over visiting Detroit.

headline.print_headline: Rangers Prevail Over Red Wings in Overtime as Lundqvist Notches Fourth Shutout
